-- U.K. Mortgage Advances Rose 4.7% in July From June, CML Says
-- B y   J e n n i f e r   R y a n
-- 2012-09-12T08:32:47Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-09-12/u-k-mortgage-advances-rose-4-7-in-july-from-june-cml-says.html
U.K. mortgage advances rose 4.7
percent in July from the previous month to 49,500, the  Council
of Mortgage Lenders  said in an e-mailed statement today.
Advances were up 5.3 percent from a year earlier, the CML said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
